OL,5, A convicted paedophile who sent a      
OL,6, picture of his erect penis to a        
OL,7, 15-year-old girl has become the first  
OL,8, person to be jailed for cyber-flashing 
OL,9, in England and Wales.                  
OL,11,FRegistered sex offender Nicholas       
OL,12,FHawkes, 39, of Basildon, Essex, also   
OL,13,Fsent unsolicited photos to a woman.    
OL,15,FThe woman took screenshots of the      
OL,16,FWhatsApp image sent on 9 February and  
OL,17,Freported it to police the same day.    
OL,19,FHawkes, who admitted two charges, has  
OL,20,Fbeen jailed for just over 15 months.   
